# Auth Setup

## Backend (FastAPI)
- JWT-based authentication (access tokens)
- OAuth support (Google)
- User, profile, and team models
- Endpoints: `/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/auth/me`, `/auth/profile`, `/auth/google`
- Tier/account type returned in `/auth/me` and `/auth/profile`

## Frontend (React)
- AuthContext manages user state, tokens, and profile
- Login/Register forms in `components/auth/`
- Google OAuth handled via popup and callback
- Auth state is refreshed after onboarding and login
- Protected routes redirect to login if unauthenticated
